{"tid":497875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【火燒北京】半夜困火場走唔甩 「低端人口」再遇劫5死9傷","createTime":"2017-12-13T08:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T17:45:20.000Z","uid":75969,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dabafd23df3af66d67247d1b2718030f294ed75d","tid":497875,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513127002_b533.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513127002_b533.jpg&h=31acef89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n習總親信、北京市委書記蔡奇強逼低端人口遷走，其中重災區之一十八里店鄉的牆子村，今日凌晨1時許一間村民自建房屋再次發生火警，當局出動9部消防車、兩個中隊前往灌救，當局稱在現場救出14人，其中5人死亡，9人受傷，已送往醫院救治。​​​​副市委書記、代市長陳吉寧日前曾經到當地巡視，檢查重大安全隱患排查清理情況。有民眾稱起火後出現極刺鼻的味道，大量電動單車、電動三輛車塞在走火通道，嚴重阻礙居民逃生。<br />\n<br />\n北京消防透過微博通報這場火災，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>僅稱火警懷疑是由電動單車起火引起</strong></span>。今早當局安排傳媒進入火場，除發現公寓內居民私自亂搭的電線橫七豎八纏繞在天花板上，狹窄的走廊堆滿雜物，隨處可見電飯煲、電暖氣等大功率電器，甚至還有幾個煤氣罐。最讓人心驚的是被燒剩骨架的電動三輪車塞在樓梯口，多部電動單車阻塞地下走廊，阻礙居民逃生。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>十八里店鄉是低端人口聚居地之一</strong></span>，位於朝陽區內，當局近日不斷驅趕低端人口，拆卸所謂的違章建築，現在村內到處都是頹垣敗瓦。蔡奇與其他北京市官員近日密集的到各低端人口村落檢查，陳吉寧曾在上月28日到十八里店鄉巡視，北京的官媒的報道稱，陳吉寧當時曾經到十八里店檢查重大安全隱患排查清理情況，當時陳稱，要以消除城市重大安全隱患、維護群眾生命安全為根本出發點和落腳點，深入細緻有序地開展專項行動，確保首都安全的底線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513148029_b2e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513148029_b2e6.jpg&h=b5a16954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513124496_d1a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513124496_d1a7.jpg&h=c547a6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171213/57574787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171213%2F57574787&d=yFsPAXzVjCh9%2FAQ%2FP3wEl5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=0eceed37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171213%2F57574787&h=5c1cb0cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171213/57574787</a><br />\n<br />\n真係咁唔好彩意外著火定係...？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7674de79b447ab2487b763b74bb8de4cfda4aa7e","tid":497875,"uid":45914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54ef2f9c9b6d354c654c1704fb92d996666bacac","tid":497875,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"火燒旺地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f138638443908d252d30d324f168c5eb13f84c18","tid":497875,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一清理低端人口就咁多火災<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有啲人特別難趕，咪用plan b囉"},{"pid":"9063170ae56665eee44a6f5ee4e30f778b2ff65c","tid":497875,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一清理低端人口就咁多火災<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有啲人特別難趕，咪用plan b囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd1047bb571d16f51acdf4ebf5a564cdb422151","tid":497875,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit